{
  "chapter": 31,
  "chapter_summary": "金鲁厄在无为厅挑战中原武林，孙倚重不敌。平凡上人突然现身，暗中指点辛捷，又当众传授新创绝招。辛捷以大衍十式与虬枝剑式融合施用，配合诘摩神步和暗香掠影，苦战百余招后终凭新招击伤金鲁厄。平凡上人携辛捷飞速离去，凌风与孙倚重追赶未果，二人途中交手后分别。凌风赶往山东林村寻找阿兰母女，却发现村庄已被黄河洪水淹没，悲痛欲绝。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "这武林之秀功力的确深厚！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "不错，我和他交过手——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "金鲁厄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方才第一仗大家有目共睹是敝师兄胜了，现在就由在下金鲁厄向中原英雄讨教第二场——",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yi_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "孙倚重",
      "listener": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "text": "在下孙倚重向金英雄讨教几招。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "金鲁厄",
      "listener": "char_sun_yi_zhong",
      "text": "你不是对手！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "金鲁厄",
      "listener": "char_sun_yi_zhong",
      "text": "你和加大尔斗斗倒是一对儿！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "好啊，娃儿，终于找到你了，快跟我走——",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "娃儿，快跟我走啊！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "我那大衍十式最近又创出一招来，极妙不可言，你快跟我去，我好教给你。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "晚辈尚要待这里的事打发了才能——",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "这里的事有什么要紧，你跟我走啊，否则我老儿可要输给那慧大师——",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里的事有什么要紧啊？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "金鲁厄",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "老匹夫不知深浅，胡言乱语些什么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "text": "你再说一遍。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "金鲁厄",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "我说你这老匹夫胡言乱语，还不给我滚开？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "text": "我老人家看你像是有甚急忙的事，你且说给我听听。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "一人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们看，你们看！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "金鲁厄",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "刚才言语冒犯，尚望前辈多多包涵，敝师兄弟此次奉师命前来完全是欣慕中原武学，敝兄弟和这些好汉已定了比武之约，原是——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来你们是要比斗的，那敢情好，快快打给我老人家看。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "金鲁厄",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "那么咱们请老前辈指正——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "捷弟，你要上去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "捷弟，还是让我试试——",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "小娃儿你自信打得赢？那蛮夷武功强得很呢。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "晚辈自忖不是对手——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你再说一遍——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "晚辈自感恐非对手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "我老儿是否曾经教过你武艺？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "前辈成全之恩晚辈永不敢忘。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "这就是了，你算得我老人家的半个徒儿，你想想平凡上人的徒儿能不如人家么？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "娃儿我看你真气直透神庭，功力似乎比在小戢岛时大有进展，你用全力打我一掌，试试你到底有多少斤两？记住，要用上全力——",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "成了，成了！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_da_er",
      "speaker_name": "加大尔",
      "listener": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "text": "希里沙，加巴罗也胡亚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_jia_da_er",
      "text": "丝巴井呼，格里摩诃尔星基。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "金鲁厄",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "老前辈歇怒，家师曾一再叮嘱他不可开罪中原前辈高人，他是浑人，前辈不要计较。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "text": "他欺我中原就没有人懂得梵语，啊，你的意思是说我以大压小，好，好，你方才不是在挑战么？我马上要我徒儿应战。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "娃儿，来，我教你一手。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "text": "有人在偷听呢，我老人家索性告诉他，看他又能奈何你！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "娃儿，好好打一架啊。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "金鲁厄",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "咱们比兵刃还是拳脚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这蛮子到底不成材，刚才若是改变鞭法，早就胜了！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "必是方才辛大侠打了这老儿一掌，这老儿就帮那蛮子，希望蛮子得胜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "金鲁厄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他这套剑法虽然高明，本来我尽挡得住，怎么一下子又多出许多变化来？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "金鲁厄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "完了，又给这厮看出我的弱点了——",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "text": "着！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_ru_sheng_yi_ren",
      "text": "着！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "娃儿，这下可真扬名立万啦——啊，险些把正事忘啦，快走——",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_ping_fan_shang_ren",
      "text": "捷弟——老前辈请等一下——",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yi_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "孙倚重",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "你跑来干么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_sun_yi_zhong",
      "text": "我原以为你追上了那老和尚和我捷弟哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yi_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "孙倚重",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "怎样，你想怎样？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_sun_yi_zhong",
      "text": "也没怎样。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yi_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "孙倚重",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "好狂的小子，在下倒要领教。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_sun_yi_zhong",
      "text": "领教！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_sun_yi_zhong",
      "text": "好功夫。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yi_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "孙倚重",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "在下身有急事，无暇逗留，他日有缘，再领教阁下高招。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "月前几场急雨，黄河水量大是增涨，终在方家村冲破河堤，淹没了全村，俺家乡离方家村不过百十里，这才带着家小……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "老伯，那林村怎样了？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng",
      "text": "客官是问高家村西五十里的林村么？如今只怕已是汪洋一片了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_a_lan",
      "text": "阿兰，阿兰，你别哭，大哥就来陪你啦！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    }
  ],
